metadata.name: ✦ Layers of Reality ✦
metadata.description:
00 We live in a digital age where Plato's "Allegory of the Cave" easily materializes in the temporary escape from reality we receive from technology. 

Over time, our minds will depend on the assistance of technology... and ultimately grow lazy.

In order for our free minds to survive, we must foster organic imagination. 

This is my first NFT on foundation. This piece is a fan art submission for avril15.NFT
